Sys::Load version 0.1
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Sys::Load is a module that is used to get the current system load.


INSTALLATION
~~~~~~~~~~~~

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES
~~~~~~~~~~~~

 - Perl 5.6.0.
 - C compiler for XS


